high_descs: Turn around and move to the television cabinet.
Pick up the cell phone from the back corner of the television cabinet.
Turn around and carry the phone to end of the sofa closest to the television.
Place the cell phone on the cushion of the sofa closest to you.
Move around the coffee table so the windows are at your back.
Pick up the cell phone from the table.
Carry the phone around the coffee table to the end of the sofa where you left the other phone.
Place the phone on the cushion of the sofa closest to you.
anns.task_desc: Move two cell phones to the sofa.

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the couch and then turn left and walk to the tv.
Pick up the phone that's to the left of the tv.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the couch.
Put the phone on the couch cushion.
Turn left and get in position to grab that phone that's on the coffee table in front of you.
Pick up the phone that's on the coffee table.
Go back to where you put put the first phone.
Put the phone next to the first one on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put two phones on the couch.

high_descs: Turn around and veer left to the TV stand.
Pick up the phone to the left of the TV stand.
Turn around and walk to the closest cushion of the couch.
Place the phone on the cushion.
Turn around and walk to the side of the coffee table closest to the fireplace.
Pick up the cell phone on the table.
Walk ahead back to the couch cushion.
Place the phone on the couch behind the other phone.
anns.task_desc: Place two cell phones on a couch.
